<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, January (Xinhua) -- The Swedish government has decided
to grant six million U.S. Dollars to Mozambique to support the
country's payment balance, a senior Mozambican official said here
today.
</P>
<P>
A communique issued by Mozambican International Cooperation
and Foreign Affair Ministry said that the Swedish government is
donating the money to "help Mozambique realize political
stability and economic development, and reduce poverty through
