<HEADLINE> Border Security Conference Opens in Chinese Capital </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 6 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese frontier guards
have made great contributions over the past five years in
safeguarding stability along the nation's extensive borders
and in vast coastal areas.
</P>
<P>
