<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, January 6 (Xinhua) -- Japan's Liberal Party (LP), a
spinoff of the New Frontier Party (NFP), held an inaugural meeting
Tuesday to elect Ichiro Ozawa as its first leader.
</P>
