local citizens, its chairman said on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Denis Chang said the seminars, organized by the IPCC for the
first time since it was set up in 1986, offered an opportunity for
the Provisional District Board and the District Fight Crime
Committee to "get to know better the current police complaints
system and the role and functions of the IPCC."
</P>
<P>
