next Monday.
</P>
<P>
Chang said the two seminars would spearhead the IPCC's
publicity drive to increase the council's transparency and public
accountability.
</P>
<P>
The IPCC, an independent advisory body with its members coming
from various sectors of the local community and authorized by the
Chief Executive of the Special Administrative Region, plays a
monitoring role in the police complaints system in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
A number of reforms have been initiated to promote the
independent status of the organization and enhance its monitoring
role over investigations of complaints directed at members of the
local police force.  
