Germany's Martina Ertl finished runner-up to the Italian in
2:21.02 while Austria's Alexandra Meissnitzer came third in
2:21.96 ahead of Germany's Katja Seizinger in 2:22.57
</P>
<P>
It was Compagnoni's fourth straight win of the season in her
favourite discipline. 
