<P>
HARARE, January 6 (Xinhua) -- More than 1,600 former freedom
fighters from Harare, Zimbabwean capital, have invested amounts
ranging between 10,000 (600 U.S. dollars) and 40,000 Zimbabwe
Dollars each into the Zimbabwe Ex-Combatants Foundation (ZECF)
with more expected to do so.
</P>
