<HEADLINE> Smits Named NBA Player of the Week </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, January 5 (Xinhua) -- The 2.24 meter tall center Rik
Smits was named NBA player of the Week on Monday after averaged 22
points and 11 rebounds in three wins for the Indiana Pacers.
</P>
