<P>
MOSCOW -- Presidents of Kyrgyzstan, Turkmenistan, Kazakhstan,
Tajikistan and Uzbekistan met in Ashgabat, Turkmenistan's capital,
on Monday, to discuss their countries' cooperations in
communications, transport, aviation and petroleum industries.
</P>
<P>
